    1 A simple JavaFX program, made for quick practice
    2 It contains a sample menu full of items you can add to your order.                                         
    3 From the users selection, and the user's selected tip, the program will then assume the tax and calculate: 
    4 - Subtotal                                                                                                 
    5 - Tip                                                                                                      
    6 - Tax                                                                                                      
    7 - Total                                             
